{"tid":1328694,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"有冇人知呢首係咩歌","createTime":"2019-07-18T03:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T10:07:09.000Z","uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f687374666d233cf7d0230eba93bcb471e9cf9e9","tid":1328694,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"好想知係咩歌但唔記得啲歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英文歌黎 好似都算新歌<br />\n唱歌個人把聲有啲似camila cabello<br />\n<br />\n旋律大約係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDo, do fa mi do, do fa mi re, do fa mi do.<br />\nDa fa mi do, do fa mi re, do fa mi do.<br />\nSo so so so la ti do&rsquo; ,<br />\nFa fa fa fa so fa mi,<br />\nRe re re re fa mi do, do fa mi re, do fa mi do.<br />\n<br />\n背景好似得支電結他彈broken chord伴奏<br />\n有冇巴絲識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dd7b7aa36e5ecc0cf7f08b93128569e6cdc300","tid":1328694,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"你係咪有音感先<br />\n如果無 就錯Q晒<br />\n我就跟足黎哼 tempo我當中間啦<br />\n哼完發覺得 都幾冷門....<br />\n幾非主流....<br />\n<br />\n快定慢歌黎"},{"pid":"c4f522d376bab6df1b7ba77f33562ec6e7e9e60e","tid":1328694,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6dd7b7aa36e5ecc0cf7f08b93128569e6cdc300","tid":1328694,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"你係咪有音感先<br />\n如果無 就錯Q晒<br />\n我就跟足黎哼 tempo我當中間啦<br />\n哼完發覺得 都幾冷門....<br />\n幾非主流....<br />\n<br />\n快定慢歌黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"肯定啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比較易認應該係呢句：<br />\n「so so so so la ti 